tool_description:
Instagram API. Get all instagram information, no proxy need. 
Scrap up to 200k Instagram profile per day. It’s capable to handle high volume.
Simple, secure and fast. Need some quick help? https://t.me/omarcosr
name: Instagram Fast
title: Instagram Fast

api_list.name: Get media data
api_list.description: Get media data by post short code or url
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://instagram-fast.p.rapidapi.com/media/CeVIU8bIhgi"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "instagram-fast.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
